Package com.spectralogic.ds3client.helpers.strategy.blobstrategy

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BlobStrategy
    An interface whose concrete implementation is used in chunk retrieval or allocation.
    BlobStrategyMaker
    An interface used as an intermediate when building a TransferStrategy instance as part of getting a transfer strategy from a TransferStrategyBuilder.
    ChunkAttemptRetryBehavior
    An interface whose concrete subclasses determine the retry behavior when a chunk operation does not complete.
    ChunkAttemptRetryDelayBehavior
    An interface whose concrete subclasses determine the delay between retries when a chunk operation does not complete.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractBlobStrategy  
    BlackPearlChunkAttemptRetryDelayBehavior
    An implementation of ChunkAttemptRetryDelayBehavior that uses the delay a Black Pearl returns in its payload when a chunk operation does not complete.
    ClientDefinedChunkAttemptRetryDelayBehavior
    An implementation of ChunkAttemptRetryDelayBehavior that uses the delay a client specifies, as opposed to using the delay a Black Pearl returns in its payload when a chunk operation does not complete.
    ContinueForeverChunkAttemptsRetryBehavior
    An implementation of ChunkAttemptRetryBehavior that will continue to retry an uncompleted chunk operation until that operation succeeds.
    GetSequentialBlobStrategy
    A subclass of BlobStrategy used in get transfers.
    MaxChunkAttemptsRetryBehavior
    A subclass of ChunkAttemptRetryBehavior that will retry an uncompleted chunk operation at most maxAttempts before giving up.
    PutSequentialBlobStrategy
    A subclass of BlobStrategy used in put transfers.
